# Security notes for this dashboard

This dashboard was generated by the `uipath-dashboards` skill. It runs inside an iframe in UiPath Automation Cloud and receives an access token from the host via postMessage.

## v1 token model

**Full user session token.** The token passed to this iframe has the same permissions as the logged-in UiPath user. If the token leaks through this dashboard, an attacker gets whatever that user can do.

## Guardrails enforced in this dashboard

- Strict CSP: `frame-ancestors` limited to UiPath cloud origins.
- Tokens are held in memory only (via the SDK's token manager). No localStorage, no cookies.
- `.env.local` (dev PAT) and `.env.production` are gitignored.
- Production build fails if `VITE_UIPATH_PAT` is set in build env (prevents bundled tokens).
- No `dangerouslySetInnerHTML`, no `console.log(sdk)`, no tokens in URLs.

## Scopes exercised

