- `OR.Folders.Read`
- `OR.Jobs.Read`

## If you edit this dashboard

Do NOT introduce any of:
- `dangerouslySetInnerHTML=` with tenant data
- `localStorage.setItem/getItem` for tokens
- `console.log(sdk)` or stringifying the SDK object
- Tokens in URL query params or `window.location.href`

Incidents: contact your UiPath admin.
